      "writtenOn": "2021-04-26T21:42:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it\u0027s a valid point. I had a same feeling that `mode_regexp` might be an overkill for the feature we want to support.\n\nI would use mode*s* instead of mode to emphasize this is a repeated field. \n\nAlso, to clarify, we would still keep `modes_exclude` so that user is able to declare something like this tryjob should not be launched in full run but can be launched in any other modes.",
